{"url": "https://www.stat.uci.edu/renewed-funding-lets-hal-stern-continue-research-of-early-life-adversity-brain-development-with-the-uci-conte-center/#more-1274", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\n<head >\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<title>Renewed Funding Lets Hal Stern Continue Research of Early-Life Adversity, Brain Development with the UCI Conte Center</title>\t\t<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"noodp,noydir\" />\n\t\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t.slide-excerpt { width: 50%; }\n\t\t\t.slide-excerpt { bottom: 0; }\n\t\t\t.slide-excerpt { left: 0; }\n\t\t\t.flexslider { max-width: 1180px; max-height: 340px; }\n\t\t\t.slide-image { max-height: 340px; }\n\t\t</style><link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//fonts.googleapis.com' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"Department of Statistics - Donald Bren School of Information &amp; Computer Sciences &raquo; Feed\" href=\"https://www.stat.uci.edu/feed/\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"Department of Statistics - Donald Bren School of Information &amp; Computer Sciences &raquo; Comments Feed\" href=\"https://www.stat.uci.edu/comments/feed/\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"Department of Statistics - Donald Bren School of Information &amp; Computer Sciences &raquo; Renewed Funding Lets Hal Stern Continue Research of Early-Life Adversity, Brain Development with the UCI Conte Center Comments Feed\" href=\"https://www.stat.uci.edu/renewed-funding-lets-hal-stern-continue-research-of-early-life-adversity-brain-development-with-the-uci-conte-center/feed/\" />\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.stat.uci.edu/renewed-funding-lets-hal-stern-continue-research-of-early-life-adversity-brain-development-with-the-uci-conte-center/\" />\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\t\twindow._wpemoj